'''Amin Sidi-Boumédiène''' (yavutse ku ya 5 Werurwe 1982), ni  umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Aligeriya|Alijeriya]] ukomoka mu bufaransa. Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa ''Al Djazira'' ngufi na firime ''Abou Leila'' . <ref>https://www.semainedelacritique.com/en/articles/interview-with-the-director-amin-sidi-boumedienne</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 5 Werurwe 1982 i [[Paris]], mu Bufaransa. <ref name="critic">https://www.semainedelacritique.com/en/directors/amin-sidi-boumediene</ref> Ariko, nyuma yakuriye mu Alger, Algeria. <ref>https://www.afriquemagazine.com/amin-sidi-boum-di-ne</ref> Yagarutse mu Bufaransa yiga chimie nyuma ya baccalauréat . <ref name="torino">http://www.torinofilmlab.it/people/5739-amin-sidi-boumediene</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yabonye impamyabumenyi iyobowe na Conservatoire Libre du Cinéma Français (CLCF) i Paris mu 2005. <ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=543948.html#:~:text=N%C3%A9%20en%201982%2C%20Amin%20Sidi,au%20Festival%20d%27Abu%20Dhabi.</ref> Noneho yakoze firime ye ya mbere ''Ejo, Algiers?'' muri 2011. <ref>http://www.zagrebfilmfestival.com/index_en.php?page=d0&iz=fpf&fid=2553</ref> <ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)</ref> Filime yatoranijwe mu birori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Hanyuma yakoze firime ye ya kabiri ''Al Djazira'', yafatiwe muri Algiers muri Nyakanga 2012.  Yatsindiye Igihembo cya Filime Nziza y'Abarabu mu iserukiramuco rya filime rya Abu Dhabi.  <ref>http://www.sanadfilmfund.com/en/archive/2011/awards</ref>

Muri 2014, yayoboye ''Serial ye ya gatatu ngufi K.'' Filime yerekanwe muminsi ya firime ya Bejaia. Nyuma yuruhererekane rwa firime ngufi zatsinze, yakoze filime yambere ''yumukobwa, Abou Leila'', film yijimye. <ref>https://www.institutfrancais.com/en/work/abou-leila-by-amin-sidi-boumediene</ref> Yarasiwe rwose mu gihugu cye cya Alijeriya. Filime yaje guhitamo kuri 58 Semaine de la Critique.  Filime yasohotse mu makinamico ku ya 15 Nyakanga 2020. <ref>https://www.francetvinfo.fr/monde/afrique/algerie/abou-leila-j-aime-beaucoup-parler-des-hommes-sensibles-de-l-algerie-explique-le-cineaste-amin-sidi-boumedienne_4045271.html</ref> Yatoranijwe kandi kugirango yerekanwe mu cyumweru mpuzamahanga cy’abanenga muri Festival ya Cannes ya 2019 . <ref>https://www.semainedelacritique.com/en/news/discover-the-selection-of-the-58supthsup-la-semaine-de-la-critique</ref> Mu Gushyingo 2019, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime nziza ya mbere ya Diregiteri mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime mpuzamahanga rya 50. <ref>https://iffigoa.org/indian-panorama-film-list-iffi-2019/</ref>

